rComments: Sharen is by far one of the nicest people I have ever met. She is extremely enthusiastic about her job, and is willing to do whatever it takes to help her students do well in the class. Very easy, you dont have to go to every class.. but make sure you get the powerpoints. Papers are extremely easy, tests are also easy if you study.

BY FAR THE BEST TEACHER EVER!! she is so incredibly nice and understanding. She gives out VERY VERY detailed study guides for exam. But you do have to study. Everything is on the study guide tho. Super easy grade. we had 3 (3page) papers and NOONE got lower than an A on any of them. LOVE HER
